high_descs: Turn around and go right to the counter with the sink.
Pick up the knife next to the salt shaker.
Turn left and walk to the white table.
Cut the yellow apple into three pieces.
Turn left and walk to then stove, then turn left again and walk forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside in front of the mug and close it.
Walk back to the white table that had the yellow apple on it.
Pickup the closest slice of yellow apple.
Walk back over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple slice to the left of the mug.
Pickup the knife from inside and close the microwave.
Turn left and walk three steps, then turn left and walk to the white table before turning left and going forward to the black stand.
Cut the yellow apple on the black stand into three slices.
Now walk back over to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside in front of the mug and apple slice and close it.
Walk over to the black stand.
Pickup the closest slice of yellow apple.
Once again walk back over to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice to the left of the apple slice inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and two apple slices from different apples inside the microwave.
